snippet.title: The Sims 3 Master Suite Stuff
snippet.description: Turn your ordinary Sim into an extraordinary dynamo with The Sims 3 Master Suite Stuff. With stylish bedroom decor, spa-inspired bathroom furnishings, intimate apparel, and eye-catchning new hairstyles, your Sims will be ready whenever the moment turns romantic.
